<article class="row hentry post-255481 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-news tag-cancer-alley tag-climate-disruption tag-environmental-racism tag-formosa tag-louisiana tag-petrochemical tag-plastics tag-rise-st-james section-environment-and-health primary_topic-environment" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-death-in-louisianas-cancer-alley-reinforces-a-small-towns-fears-of-industry-impacts/" title="A Death in Louisiana&#8217;s Cancer Alley Reinforces a Small Town&#8217;s Fears of Industry Impacts">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/2017_0404dermansky1-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="Keith Hunter, long-time resident of St. James, Louisiana, in March 2017, roughly a year before he died." loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/2017_0404dermansky1-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/2017_0404dermansky1-200x150.jpg 200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/environment-and-health/' rel='section' class='environment-and-health' style='color: #0ba864;'>Environment &amp; Health</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/a-death-in-louisianas-cancer-alley-reinforces-a-small-towns-fears-of-industry-impacts/">A Death in Louisiana&#8217;s Cancer Alley Reinforces a Small Town&#8217;s Fears of Industry Impacts</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Helping the residents of St. James relocate seems more feasible than assuring them that the air they are breathing is clean.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/julie-dermansky/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Julie Dermansky</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.desmogblog.com/2018/03/31/death-louisiana-cancer-alley-reinforces-st-james-fears-industry-impacts/' itemprop='url'>DeSmogBlog</a></span></dd>
</dl>
