<div class="testimonial-wrapper">
<div class="testimonial-header">
<p align="right" style="margin-top: 3.5em; color: #1383bf; font-weight: 600; font-size: 28px;">Shine a light on government and corporate exploitation</p>
<p align="right" style="margin-top: .75em; color: #000000; font-weight: 400; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.35em;">When it comes to waging war, stripping basic rights, election fraud, or a global health crisis, <span style="color:#1383bf;">you deserve the truth.</span> </p>
